name: Pollen #017 (Brunhild)
description: Brunhild was once a fierce warrior who led her sisters into battle to protect the Pollen Kingdom. She knows how to use a sword and shield and can cast battle magic to help her allies. Queen Lamia has always been jealous of Brunhild's proficiency in battle, and can't wait for the opportunity to burn her to the ground. ~ pollenkingdom.com
